dc_title_s: Water snake recapture and morphometric data
dc_description_s: These are long-term capture/recapture and morphometric data for northern watersnakes (Nerodia sipedon) from two sites at QUBS: Barb's Marsh (44 31'25.52"N 76 22'25.60"W), Beaver Marsh (44 31'22.65"N 76 23'17.87"W). These data were collected as part of the doctoral thesis of Greg Brown, under supervision of Pat Weatherhead, then of Carleton University. Pat Weatherhead and Greg Brown share IP rights on these.
